To connect to a machine using a public IP and a PEM file, you can create an SSH config file to simplify the process


Locate ur pem file

create an ssh file 

vi ~/.ssh/config


Add the configuration: Add the following configuration to the SSH config file:

Host your_host_name
    HostName your_public_ip
    User your_username
    IdentityFile /path/to/your.pem


    